      <main class="px-3 col-8 offset-2">

        <h2 class = "guidelines">Guidelines</h2>

        <p class = "lead">
          This website lists original stories that are freely and legally available online. This does not include fanfiction or stories that are missing early chapters (stubs). It also does not include stories that have been translated to English and posted online. 

         </p>
         <p class = "text-center"> _</p>

         <p class = "lead">
          Once you have signed up and verified your email you can add and review stories and rank other users' reviews. You do not need to be the author to add a story, but please check to ensure that a story is not listed and that it meets these guidelines before trying to add it.
         </p>
         <p class = "text-center"> _</p>
         <!-- <p class = "lead">
          Each story will be reviewed by a moderator before it is added to ensure that it meets our content policy. This means it may take some time for your new addition to show up.
         </p> -->
         <!-- <p class = "text-center"> _</p> -->
         <h4>Content Policy</h4>
         <p class = "lead">
          Images should not contain graphic violence, nudity, or explicit content. Reviews and story descriptions should not contain explicit language, profanity, hate speech, or harrassment.          </p>
          <p class = "text-center"> _</p>

        <p class = "lead">
        Artificially manipulating fiction scores and rankings is prohibited.       </p>
        <p class = "text-center"> _</p>
        <h4>Target Audience and Warnings</h4>
        <p class = "lead">
         Reviewers are invited to make an estimate for a story's target audience, ranging from appropriate for everyone (10+), teens, or mature audiences. Reviewers are also invited to provide content warnings using the same scale for graphic violence, sexual content, and profanity. </p>
        <p class = "text-center"> _</p>


     
